name: The End
description:
this is the end from the previous artworks. each story has a silver lining about how she can survive from living in the catastrophe. how she keep fighting againts her own fear, hatred, anger that almost put her into a catatonic state. revenge keep burning her deep down of the soul which is almost killing her inside. until she can put all of her nightmare to fire just to get her freedom for living in peace although it might hurt her once again.
The End (at least)
